                {
                    "name": "The Firebleeder's Mark",
                    "type": "sidebar",
                    "text": "Terrible rumors speak of other monsters that have emerged from the Firebleeder\u2019s corpse in the centuries since the Legion of Wands put the beast to rest. Reports of massive clouds of noxious black sand, gray-blooded gnoll zombies with spider-like limbs, and guttural, otherworldly howls during harvest moons have long fueled local rumors that more terrors lurk in the valleys of the Brazen Peaks than a single dead god-spawn.",
